 <instruction>hakch das chlain</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>meng gesnitten <ingredient en="bacon" commodity="Q11106">spekch</ingredient> darczu roche <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613">ayr</ingredient> vnd <ingredient en="saffron" commodity="Q25434">Saffran</ingredient></instruction>
 vnd <instruction>mach denn pellein als die <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613" ana="comparison">ayr</ingredient></instruction>
 vnd <instruction>pach sy In der <ingredient en="stock" commodity="Q3075310">Suppen</ingredient> in einem <tool en="bowl" commodity="Q153988">char</tool> </instruction>
vnd <instruction><time>wenn Sy erhertten</time> So erwell sy In dem <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613">ayr</ingredient> <ingredient en="batter" commodity="Q29493">taig</ingredient></instruction>
 <instruction>Stozz sy an einen <tool en="spit" commodity="Q20181361">spis</tool></instruction>
 <instruction>prat Sy</instruction>
 <closer>gib Sy hin</closer></div></body></text></TEI>